  <section class="service-content">
    <h2>Serving {city} and All of {county}</h2>
    
    <p>Crystal River's mix of waterfront properties, established neighborhoods, and rural acreage creates diverse concrete needs. Our team has worked on everything from small residential walkways to large commercial projects throughout the area. This experience means we understand what works in Citrus County's unique environment.</p>

    <h3>Understanding {city}'s Terrain</h3>
    
    <p>Crystal River sits in a region known for its springs and waterways. This creates interesting soil and groundwater conditions that affect concrete work. Properties near the springs may have high water tables, while areas to the east tend toward the sandy soils typical of Central Florida.</p>
    
    <p>Our site assessment process identifies these conditions before we begin work. We adjust our techniques accordingly—whether that means additional drainage provisions, modified concrete mixes, or enhanced reinforcement. The result is concrete that performs well regardless of where your property is located.</p>

    <h3>Residential Concrete Excellence</h3>
    
    <p>Most of our Crystal River work involves residential projects. Homeowners throughout the area trust us for:</p>
    
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Driveway replacement:</strong> Many Crystal River homes have aging driveways that detract from curb appeal and create safety concerns.</li>
      <li><strong>Patio installation:</strong> With Crystal River's wonderful climate, outdoor living spaces are practically essential. We create patios that extend your living area outdoors.</li>
      <li><strong>Pool deck upgrades:</strong> If your pool deck is cracked, stained, or outdated, we can install a fresh surface that's both beautiful and safe.</li>
      <li><strong>Walkways and steps:</strong> From front walks to garden paths, we create concrete surfaces that are functional and attractive.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Commercial Concrete Services</h3>
    
    <p>Crystal River's downtown and commercial areas also require quality concrete work. We serve businesses throughout the area with parking lot installation and repair, ADA-compliant sidewalks, loading areas, and foundation work. Our commercial projects meet all applicable codes and standards while delivering the durability businesses need.</p>

    <h3>Rural and Agricultural Concrete</h3>
    
    <p>Beyond the city proper, Citrus County includes extensive rural areas where concrete needs differ from suburban properties. We specialize in pole barn foundations, equipment pads, agricultural building slabs, and other applications common on larger properties. If you have acreage in the Crystal River area, we can handle your concrete needs.</p>

    <h3>Get Started Today</h3>
    
